  "texts": [
    "But is it also useful?",
    "To answer this question, a systematic literature review integrated the findings of 68 empirical user studies that assessed how saliency maps affect human performance.",
    "While some performance benefits were evident, null effects were even more frequent and performance costs were not uncommon.",
    "Moreover, characteristic biases were observed.",
    "For instance, saliency maps led people to infer that the AI is correct and thus agree with its predictions even when these predictions were incorrect or uncertain."
